== Specifications ==
The iPhone 16 and 16 Plus will get a vertical camera layout, similar to the [[iPhone 12]]. Apple used a diagonal layout for [[iPhone 13]], [[iPhone 14]], and [[iPhone 15]], and no one knows why these models will switch back.

